17
00:02:21.988 --> 00:02:23.365
Don't worry.

18
00:03:52.621 --> 00:03:55.332
Hi, Ruja. It's me, Wichai.

19
00:03:56.166 --> 00:03:57.542
Your dad's friend.

20
00:03:58.126 --> 00:03:59.211
Remember me?

21
00:04:01.004 --> 00:04:03.340
